<swapmax> - swap maxed link unit for unmaxed unit during "farm links". (OFF by default)
<zeniendlv> - set EZA end level for "farm zeni".
<autosupport> - automatically select support leader. (OFF by default)
<babafp> - auto baba only SSRs on FP banner. (OFF by default)
<bonus> - auto build team with only bonus units. (OFF by default)
